name: Lowtech Archeotech Blueprint Package
desc: Enables heavy industry to construct lost weapons and ships from the low-tech area. Archeotech weapons have often better range and damage output than actual weapons used in the sector at the cost of flux efficiency, turn rate and accuracy.
